  [1;34m"body"[m[1;37m:[m [32m"## Descripción\nImplementa un sistema inteligente de descargas que:\n- Detecta la plataforma del usuario (Android/Windows/Linux/Desktop) desde el User-Agent\n- Verifica si existe el archivo `.iflapp` para la plataforma antes de mostrarlo\n- Muestra descarga directa cuando está disponible\n- Ofrece alternativas (código fuente, otras versiones) cuando no hay coincidencia directa\n\n## Cambios\n- `app.py`: Nuevas funciones `get_release_info()`, `check_iflapp_exists()`, `get_download_for_platform()`\n- `templates/download.html`: Actualizado para usar `download_info` con lógica condicional\n\n## Comportamiento\n| Plataforma | Resultado |\n|------------|-----------|\n| Android | Muestra comando curl para Termux |\n| Windows/Linux | Verifica si existe `.iflapp` → muestra o alternativas |\n| Desktop | Muestra alternativas con versiones disponibles |\n\n## Testing\n- Probado con User-Agent de Desktop → muestra alternativas\n- Probado con User-Agent de Android → muestra Termux\n\n@JesusQuijada34 can click here to [continue refining the PR](https://app.all-hands.dev/conversations/ffda4a9c-2d61-4368-8b67-d55ec235233f)\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Added a multilingual web UI with refreshed home, download, FAQ, release notes, reporting, admin reports, stats, and error pages.\n  * Introduced PWA support with a web app manifest and offline caching via a service worker.\n  * Added Telegram-backed support workflows, including webhook setup and owner notifications.\n  * Improved download selection using GitHub release/version discovery and platform-aware URL reachability checks.\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Added visit analytics tracking and language persistence across navigation.\n* **Tests**\n  * Added homepage integration tests for language and content rendering.\n* **Chores**\n  * Updated deployment/startup via Procfile/run_all.sh and pinned dependencies.\n* **Revert / Removal**\n  * Removed the previous updater/install functionality.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->"[m[1;37m,[m
